INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('77311a23-c6e0-4617-8f89-cc8b726cf2a9', '科技', '6', '审核中', '阿里创投换女掌门，马云教过的最后一届同学，从小客服做到总裁', 'd1520de1-d496-45a2-8cc6-73ff1803c871.jpg', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">40亿，能买多少梅干菜？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">作为中国最大的互联网产业资本的领头羊，阿里在投资界的一举一动都备受关注。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">3月8日，杭州阿里巴巴创业投资管理有限公司发生工商信息变更，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">阿里巴巴集团CEO张勇不再担任阿里创投法人以及董事长，阿里巴巴B2B事业群总裁戴珊接任。</span></p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/b067215e-cfca-4cc7-85dd-9d3e06fa6fa1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">对此，阿里巴巴和媒体回应称，此举是一个常规的公司管理动作。<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">戴珊在此次调整后还将担任阿里创投的总经理一职。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">说起戴珊其人，她的经历可以说也是十分传奇。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">在阿里，她花名苏荃，工号11，阿里人称之“MM”。</span>从工号来看，也可以知道，这是阿里巴巴集团的骨灰级元老人物。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">没错，她就是当初的阿里“十八罗汉”之一。毕业后跟随马云，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">从最初一个小小的客服开始，一路成长为如今独当一面的女强人。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">今天，我们就来了解一下，这位阿里创投的新掌门人——戴珊。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">马云的最后一届学生</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">坚信：人要有梦想</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">在马云还是教师的时候，他教的最后一届学生，戴珊便是其中之一。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">在授学的那一年中，他常常鼓励自己的学生：<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">做人一定要有梦想。</span>彼时的戴珊，便深受这句话的影响。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">次年，马云辞职了，奔向他的梦想之路，开始了创业的生涯。而这时，戴珊也正好毕业，深受尊师影响的她，出于对马云的信任，义无反顾地假如了马云的创业团队。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">那时的她，坚信马云的梦想一定能实现，也深信自己的选择是正确的。怀揣着一颗梦想之心，她开始了属于她的传奇。</span></p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/f97e15ea-fcfc-4c05-b6b1-a62332318a39.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">戴珊最初的岗位是客服。尽管如此，她并没有气馁，客服工作一直做得很投入，无论多晚都要回复客户。还一度由于邮件回复得非常快，被客户怀疑<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">她们</span>的真实存在。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">那时的她，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">每个月就拿500块钱的工资，</span>干的工作也看起来似乎没什么地位，但是凡事都喜欢做好的她却还是十分的拼。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">即便身体柔弱，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">也坚持每天工作16到18小时，累了就睡在办公室的睡袋里，吃饭基本就是3块钱的盒饭。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">有一天，爱吃梅干菜的戴珊在湖畔花园民房里吃着盒饭，突然对大家说，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">“等我有钱了，我就去买一屋子的梅干菜！”</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">多么单纯的想法呀！那时的她，还尚且稚嫩，只凭着一股能坚持的精神，因马云那句“人一定要有梦想”，陪伴着阿里一路成长至今。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/b8e37731-1fc6-4054-8a33-2653bfcb41ab.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">有钱后，戴珊有没有买一屋子的梅干菜，我们不知道。但是我们如今看到的，是开了挂般晋升的戴珊，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">她如今的身价为40亿。如果要买梅干菜，或许可以围上地球半个圈。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">那个柔弱温婉的女子，因为她对阿里的坚守，因为“怀揣着梦想”，成长了为如今<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">独挡一面</span>的女强人。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">去年，教师节那天，戴珊动情地感慨道：（马云）老师，果真梦想还是要有的。</span></p><p><br></p>', '2019-03-16 11:38:08', null, '0', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('821eec65-cc7e-4d72-9993-7bdba9480965', '游戏', '3', '已发表', '熊猫TV破产，IG战队又该怎么办？王思聪：都安排好了', '637bf513-31df-4340-afcb-3e53584239dc.jpg', '<blockquote style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; position: relative; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background: rgb(244, 245, 246); border-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">大家好，这里是超人电竞，我是超人，一个实力与颜值并存的游戏爱好者！谢谢各位小伙伴的阅读与观看，喜欢超人的可以点关注一起游戏一起上分。</blockquote><h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 36px; margin-bottom: 22px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">熊猫TV破产，IG战队又该怎么办，王思聪：都安排好了</h1><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">说起现在的很多直播平台，相信很多人对于这些在网上有着很多人气的新兴产业一定都是不会感觉到陌生吧，也是有很多人都是非常的喜欢在自己闲暇无事的时候，通过在直播平台上看一些感兴趣的直播来放松自己。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/01055c65-6d5d-4cd8-9a58-5df0eb5abcd1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">相信很多人应该也都是会在一些直播平台上经常看一些自己感兴趣的直播吧，也是有很多非常受人喜欢的主播和网红，而经常看直播的人们对于熊猫TV这个非常火热的直播平台一定都是不会感觉到陌生吧。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/6fd35d61-09ef-4387-b789-4aeebb614f9e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">也是有很多人都是非常喜欢，更是我们都是非常熟悉的王思聪王校长一手创办起来的直播平台，可以说是他旗下的一个比较重要的产业之一了，也是现在风头正盛的IG战队的选手们平常直播的一个平台。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/b2ef8680-2bd4-447b-836b-dd9599e81be1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">相信很多人对于这个平台应该也都是非常的熟悉了，尤其是在去年2018年IG战队又是在英雄联盟2018年全球总决赛之中不负众望的成功的为我国拿下了第一个世界冠军，也是吸引了很多人的注意力。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/7ce2018a-5085-418a-b9d0-adf868fb4d1a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">更是让很多人都是非常的关注他们，按说也是应该顺势的带动直播平台的发展，毕竟IG战队的老板也是我们的王校长，对于冠军队伍肯定是会有很多人的关注的，也应该是可以吸引不少人才对。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/50261841-6ce6-450d-a5cb-9dd59aed1783.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">但是结果却是并不是那样，相信很多人应该也是发现了，熊猫TV的影响力和火爆程度也是完全不如当初了，情况可以说是每况日下，很多知名板块的主播也是都被挖走了。</p><p><br></p>', '2019-03-16 04:13:19', null, '66', '134', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('8340357b-9882-4dc7-a87b-acdbd4a65687', '体育', '2', '已发表', '霸气！连取6分逆转击溃韩国二单 林丹挺进八强将遭遇印尼一哥', 'af2ec143-76c0-4a39-9448-de733ddb7110.jpg', '<div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/6be55de5-ba7b-49a4-b6d6-d797ea995079.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2019年世界羽联世界巡回赛瑞士公开赛结束第二轮，中国队有多人进入八强。林丹2比0获胜，他携手石宇奇进入男单八强，陈清晨/贾一凡和李汶妹/郑雨一同闯入女双四分之一决赛。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">林丹第二轮遇到韩国的李东根，两人此前的10次交手林丹9胜1负，不过在去年的美国公开赛上，林丹不敌李东根，这是他首次输给对手，李东根目前世界排名是第28位，是韩国男单排名第二的球员。首局的3平后林丹连续得分领跑，李东根迅速追成8平。林丹还击4分再次拉开，李东根很快又追成13平并反超。在李东根以19比15领先后，林丹掀起反扑攻势，一口气连得6分，他以21比19逆转拿下。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">第二局林丹以4比1、8比4开局，李东根之后曾两次把差距缩小到1分，林丹都给予还击保持领跑位置。在19比17领先后，林丹一口气连得2分以21比17再下一城，他以2比0淘汰李东根晋级。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/b3ea0667-bd54-4c95-9f81-d9f2021dbf64.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">头号种子石宇奇迎战世界排名第60位的巴西球员科埃霍。首局两人争夺激烈，场上连续战平，15平后科埃霍发力连得4分拉开领跑。石宇奇还击1分，科埃霍又拿2分以21比16先拔头筹。之后的比赛石宇奇逐渐掌控局势，他在大部分时间里都比分领先，他以21比15、21比11连扳两局，从而以2比1逆转战胜科埃霍晋级。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">四分之一决赛里，石宇奇将对阵卡尔乔维，林丹将遭遇4号种子印尼的金廷，谌龙将对阵印度的德伊。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/bac266ca-ab24-402c-b352-0f56a1dcef60.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">女双第二轮里中国队有喜有忧。头号种子陈清晨/贾一凡保持强势，她们只用了36分钟就以2比0（21比17、21比14）击败印尼的伊玛努埃拉/拉马汉迪。李汶妹/郑雨经过58分钟激战打满三局，她们以2比1（21比19、16比21、21比16）淘汰日本的荒木茜羽/今井莉子。陈露/徐涯抵抗了40分钟后以0比2（7比21、12比21）不敌4号种子韩国的张艺娜/郑景银。</p>', '2019-03-16 04:05:37', null, '87', '312', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('8904dc93-fece-470e-8108-55e224b80185', '娱乐', '5', '已发表', '章子怡亲自撕下了她的“国际章”面具', 'fcac7bd9-27e3-4023-b31e-e817e657b450.jpg', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">40岁仍能被称为“女神”的，章子怡算一个。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/515141dd-ba69-4173-82f4-04681063ee22.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">在<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">@头条娱乐</span>举办的<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">#最美的她#</span>活动中，章子怡入围十大“最美”女星，然而目前她的票数仅超谢娜。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/5c8b53e8-57f8-4d90-8538-e5847f0e3e97.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">可这并不影响章子怡在很多人心目中“最美”的印象。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">《妻子的浪漫旅行2》买超向张嘉倪求婚的片段，甜到了不少人。与之同时登上热搜的，还有汪峰向章子怡的求婚画面。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">再次回忆起当时场景的章子怡，嘴角还是会不自觉地露出甜蜜的微笑。与汪峰结婚这四年，章子怡一直受到质疑：一个国际巨星，为什么最后会选择嫁给一个普普通通的摇滚歌手？</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/0e866525-79a1-41d1-bfd5-000f915ceb62.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">不仅是她的婚姻，章子怡在确认参加《妻子的浪漫旅行2》时，也是不被理解的。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">她一直被认为是走在国际影视行业前沿的“开路人”。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/cb15c9c0-64f6-47e7-a186-ef00382f4aaf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">百花奖最佳女主角、华表奖优秀女演员、金像奖最佳女主角、金球奖最佳女主角提名……章子怡是很多人心目中只演“最高逼格”作品的女演员，自从她正式进军好莱坞之后，“国际章”这个称呼就一直冠以其名。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/b1bd6f3c-27fa-4f8c-a662-d2b39230e003.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">她怎么能“下凡”来参加这样“自毁形象”的节目？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">“国际章”</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">章子怡在17岁的时候，就主演了她的第一部电影《星星点灯》，通过这部电影成功进入演艺圈的她，也开始了在中央戏剧学院表演系正式学习的普通人生。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/de2d7546-8360-4325-8b88-cb7c5efd574b.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">如果说章子怡人生发生巨大转折，那和张艺谋的“慧眼识珠”是分不开的。19岁，她就通过张艺谋电影《我的父亲母亲》中招娣这个角色，拿下了第23届大众电影百花奖最佳女主角。</p><p><br></p>', '2019-03-16 03:53:13', null, '31', '444', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('94568dd9-da84-4fec-bb76-017e019a0c27', '科技', '6', '草稿', '十大机械设计软件特点对比，作为设计师不懂也要了解一下', 'e09fd8ca-34e9-45f1-acba-d619da511300.jpg', '<h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 36px; margin-bottom: 22px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">在机械设计软件里面，UG、Pro/E与CATIA三分天下，方便易用还是SW。做机械设计这一行，最离不开的就是各种软件，而设计决定了实际产品的性能，因此需要采用软件进行辅助和系统分析。市面上并没有一款十全十美的软件，都各有特点和长处，在此我们就盘点一下比较常用的十款软件。</h1><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">一、Pro/EngineerPro/Engineer</span></p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/dfb725c3-a43a-41b2-835f-cc268ae115f5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Pro/EngineerPro/Engineer是美国PTC公司旗下的CAD/CAM/CAE一体化三维软件，是参数化技术的最早应用者，在目前的三维造型软件领域中占有着重要地位，特别是在国内产品设计领域使用广泛。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">使用特点：Pro/Engineer第一个提出了参数化设计的概念，并且采用了单一数据库来解决特征的相关性问题。所谓单一数据库，就是工程中的资料全部来自一个库，使得每一个独立用户在为一件产品造型而工作，不管是哪一个部门的。换言之，在整个设计过程的任何一处发生改动，亦可以前后反应在整个设计过程的相关环节上。另外，Pro/E采用模块化方式，用户可以根据自身的需要进行选择，而不必安装所有模块。Pro/E的基于特征方式，能够将设计至生产全过程集成到一起，实现并行工程设计，不但可以应用于工作站，而且也可以应用到单机上。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">二、SolidWorks</span></p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/c502fe70-8582-444f-8f46-3819253263ef.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">SolidWorks软件是世界上第一个基于Windows开发的三维CAD系统，能够在整个产品设计的工作中，SolidWorks完全自动捕捉设计意图和引导设计修改。在SolidWorks的装配设计中可以直接参照已有的零件生成新的零件，所以不论用“自顶而下”方法还是“自底而上”的方法进行装配设计，都能提高效率。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">使用特点：SolidWorks Premium 提供了强大易用的功能，可以自动完成任务、理顺工作流程并快速定义和验证设计的形状、配合和功能。作为SOLIDWORKS 产品开发解决方案（涵盖设计、仿真、可持续性、技术交流 和 数据管理）的组成部分，SolidWorks Premium 还提供专门工具支持创新设计，从而有助于高效的设计决策。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">三、Mastercam</span></p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/17e037ea-11a9-4262-a2d7-28a753a3701b.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Mastercam集二维绘图、三维实体造型、曲面设计、体素拼和、数控编程、刀具路径模拟及真实感模拟等多种功能于一身，提供了设计零件外形所需的理想环境，可设计出复杂的曲线、曲面零件。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">使用特点：Mastercam具有强大的曲面粗加工及灵活的曲面精加工功能。其可靠刀具路径效验功能可模拟零件加工的整个过程，模拟中不但能显示刀具和夹具与被加工零件的干涉、碰撞情况，真实反映加工过程中的实际情况。同时Mastercam对系统运行环境要求较低，在造型设计、CNC铣床、CNC车床或CNC线切割等加工操作中都能获得最佳效果。</span></p><p><br></p>', '2019-03-16 10:51:42', null, '0', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('951ceaa6-b40c-4f70-a574-77604026eddd', '游戏', '3', '已发表', '早已被“淘汰”的低配置游戏，现如今还有人在坚持玩，至高的经典', '76428333-a233-4a50-a713-160eac78f3fd.jpg', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">各位大佬兄弟姐妹们，你们好呀，今天小老弟给大家带来的文章内容是：“早已被“淘汰”的低配置游戏，现如今还有人在坚持玩，至高的经典”毕竟每个人口味不一样，请各位网友有任何疑问评论到后方给予我写文章的动力，小编会做到最好的，感谢各位支持</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/806092d7-4846-4e07-8ba7-b7a223c06f53.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">使命召唤6：使命召唤系列的每一部都比较不错了，但是使命召唤6虽然好玩，但是配置都是淘汰掉的了，还是使命召唤4这些都是，但是依旧好玩，小编也一直在玩哟。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/561187fd-aab5-4c7e-9280-e3b16a1b325f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">功夫熊猫：这是根据电影改编的一个游戏，可以说玩这个游戏真的是非常的心累，不知道各位有没有这样觉得呢，总觉得打斗非常少，不过还是觉得好玩呢。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/cd95bba5-2e98-43a0-bbe9-afeaeacfc929.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">反恐精英起源：相比大家都玩过反恐精英1.6吧，那可是至高无上的经典了，但是画面基本上没有起源好，当时很多人认为起源已经是高配置了，但是现在已经被淘汰掉了。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/4e5fc62f-d7c7-4c10-bf6b-0d34e176b947.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">不知道各位条友还有没有在玩那些已经过时却非常好玩的游戏呢？可以在评论中分享哦，小编我发完这篇文章就要默默地打开尘封已经的红色警戒共和国之辉去屠城了哈哈，然后下午继续cs啪啪啪，拜拜咯。</p><p><br></p>', '2019-03-16 04:09:38', null, '78', '879', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('98b0d9e9-e0bc-4d3e-bba2-b58b3bed957c', '科技', '6', '已撤回', '三月都是小打小闹，四月新机潮，4款重磅新机联袂登场', 'fde80b37-845b-496b-878e-a8e31eecaa1e.jpg', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">华为P30Pro</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">华为P30Pro已经宣布将在这个月月底的时候海外发布，而它的国行发布会应该就在4月份了。从目前曝光的情况来看，华为P30Pro和华为P20Pro一样都是一款主打拍照的手机，10倍混合变焦会是华为P30Pro这款手机最大的亮点。因为华为P20Pro在去年以109分霸榜DxO后，华为P30Pro可以在今年拉开友商多少分数成为了很多人关注的点。不过从外媒曝光的消息来看，华为P30Pro在拍照上会相当给力，而且华为P30Pro的黑科技不仅仅是拍照，让人期待。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/960f6801-2106-408a-bbef-1cf2d6381c60.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">OPPO Reno</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">OPPO Reno是OPPO最近刚刚宣布的一个新系列，不出意外应该会和iQOO一样主打性价比。虽然沈义人说性价比是一个伪命题，但是从目前的情况来看，OPPO Reno基本上就是一款3000出头的骁龙855旗舰。设计的话OPPO Reno的背部设计已经曝光了，整体颜值可以说相当不错的，不过在OPPO Reno上，我似乎看到了魅族的影子。虽然OPPO Reno不会有极致的性价比，但是OPPO已经承诺Reno将会有大量备货，也就是说你想买OPPO Reno就可以买OPPO Reno，这绝对是OPPO Reno最吸引人的地方。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/1f12e88e-7532-4852-9fff-01135ea5796e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">魅族16s</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">前段时间，黄章已经在论坛上暗示魅族将在4月份的时候发布魅族16s。虽然黄章之前说魅族16s要5月份的时候才会发，但是看着友商们玩得热火朝天，魅族自然也不甘寂寞。而且对于魅族16s这款偏保守的产品，越早发布对它来说肯定越有利。作为一款小改款的手机，魅族16s在整体设计上基本和魅族16一致，不过上下边框会进一步收窄，摄像头也会从原来的双摄变到主流的三摄像头。可以说，虽然魅族16s看起来是一款一厘米进步的产品，但是在极致设计和短板补足之后，它可能又会是一个小米9杀手。</p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/8b10ae16-7696-4535-b474-16e30af55e9e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">荣耀20</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">荣耀20这款手机刚刚被曝光出来，虽然只有一张背面照，但是我们也基本可以猜出荣耀20的大概。水滴屏幕的设计，麒麟980处理器，屏幕指纹+后置三摄的设计，这也是今年上半年性价比手机的标配。而且在定位更高的荣耀V20卖2999元的情况下，荣耀20的价格很可能会控制在2799元，而如果荣耀20真的卖这个价格的话，那它在国内手机市场上可能会打败小米9，成为消费者最喜欢的性价比旗舰。毕竟在现货能力上，这几年来的荣耀都做得比小米良心。</p><p><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/1a5bc9d0-ee89-4e28-8508-7d7654e54785.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></p>', '2019-03-16 03:21:05', null, '33', '21', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('a15832a0-2454-4ede-b1d5-9bd76247f645', '科技', '6', '已发表', '左手京东，右手神舟：历时一个半月，“扑朔迷离”的后续来了', 'c6fe1f5f-db7e-4b34-8dba-7218dc69b4eb.jpg', '<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">一个半月之前，网购电脑送修，期间百折千回。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">东哥在头条发了一篇文章，引发了大家关注，纷纷要求有了结果说一下。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">这两天终于有了结果，借</font>“315”这个好日子，说给大家听听，也给遇到网络电脑售后情况的兄弟们一个借鉴（</span><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:bold;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">文章有点长，细节有点细，但是包你爱不释手</font></span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">）。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"http://localhost:1111/NewsImg/972a902d-3801-4b39-b30e-60d5d4b8a7c1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><br></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">电脑是从京东网购的一台神舟的笔记本电脑，购买时间</font>2017年11月1日。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\">2018年暑假，电脑出现不能开机情况，联系寻找本地维修点无果（是不存在，神舟的维修网点该更新更新了）。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">无果第二天，无意间按下开机，启动成功，遂以为没有问题，邮寄给了远在数千里外求学的孩子。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">然而孩子寒假回来却告诉我，说独立显卡邮寄过去就不能用了，一直凑合着。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:bold;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">到这个节点，电脑整机保修一年已经过期，但是主要部件保修为两年或者三年</font>——同时提醒大家，坏了及时送修，整机保修期应该更主动一些。</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">联系了京东的客服，建议东哥联系售后。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:12.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(34,34,34);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-styl